            "title": "Living with voracious roommates: Factors that explain isotopic niche variation in a mixed colony of insectivorous bats",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Isaac",
                    "lastName": "Peña‐Villalobos"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
