            "title": "Birds and bats captured in a managed forest in Southwestern Brazilian Amazonia: Results and recommendations from a short-term study",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Diego",
                    "lastName": "Pedroza"
